<title>JAPAN: Kajima shares hit year new low for 1997.</title>
<headline>Kajima shares hit year new low for 1997.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-04-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in Kajima Corp on Tuesday fell to a new low for calendar 1997, as selling continued to batter Japan's debt-ridden contruction sector, traders said.</p>
<p>The share price briefly hit a low of 479 before recovering to 492, down 37 yen, by 0145 GMT. Its previous low for the year of 511 was set on Monday.</p>
